summary:
I'm the founder of Numbered - a full-service creative agency working with fashion, tech & lifestyle brands. We collaborate closely with our clients to tell their stories, engaging audiences by building beautiful experiences & products. 

Since 2009, I've been designing for prestigious clients such as MTV, Chanel, Uniqlo, Kenzo, Ed Banger, Louis Vuitton, Made.com, Hermes, Ysl, Canal+, Lacoste, Ami Paris, Sézane ... Working with talented teams, allowed us to proudly win FWA, AWWWARDS, Cannes Lions, Cristal, Stratégies and Webby awwards.
